<https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3AaBi-mw11185.5#sense-ap90-1> a ontolex:LexicalSense ;
  ontolex:isSenseOf <https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3AaBi-mw11185.5> ;
  csl:sourceDictionary "ap90" ;
  skos:definition "It means ‘to’, ‘towards’, ‘in the direction of’; go towards,; ‘for’, ‘against’; ‘on’, ‘upon’; to sprinkle on;, ‘over’, ‘above’, ‘across’; to overpower,; ‘greatly’; ‘excessively’"@en .

<https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3AaBi-mw11185.5#sense-ap90-2> a ontolex:LexicalSense ;
  ontolex:isSenseOf <https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3AaBi-mw11185.5> ;
  csl:sourceDictionary "ap90" ;
  skos:definition "It expresses intensity or superiority; ‘supreme duty’; ‘very red, ‘very new’; ‘towards,’ ‘in the direction of,’ forming compounds"@en .

<https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3AaBi-mw11185.5#sense-ap90-3> a ontolex:LexicalSense ;
  ontolex:isSenseOf <https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3AaBi-mw11185.5> ;
  csl:sourceDictionary "ap90" ;
  skos:definition "It means towards, in the direction or vicinity of; in, above, aloft, on the top, (mostly Ved)"@en .

<https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3AaBi-mw11185.5#sense-ap90-4> a ontolex:LexicalSense ;
  ontolex:isSenseOf <https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3AaBi-mw11185.5> ;
  csl:sourceDictionary "ap90" ;
  skos:definition "To, towards, in the direction of, against; (with or in in this sense); or;,; Near, before, in front or presence of; On, upon, with regard or <lbi"@en .

<https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3AaBi-mw11185.5#sense-fri-1> a ontolex:LexicalSense ;
